channel.title: Compile error
channel.description: Hey, i am using project 16 and i have edited loads on the client.java, everytime i click the compile i get a error saying 'Javac' is not a recognized internal or external command. I have checked all the paths to my java folder but i dont seem to see the javac file? only the java.exe do i need to download another version of java if so can anyone help me download this with a link?

item.title: Compile error
item.dc:creator: @flamed_fury1 flamed fury1
item.description:
@flamed_fury1 wrote:

@echo off
title yourservername [COMPILER]
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_07\bin\java.exe” server
pause

Hope this helps.
